foods.ingredients: ENRICHED WHEAT FLOUR (FLOUR, ENZYME, ASCORBIC ACID [DOUGH CONDITIONER], NIACIN, REDUCED IRON, THIAMINE MONONITRATE, RIBOFLAVIN, FOLIC ACID), WATER, BROWN SUGAR, HIGH FRUCTOSE CORN SYRUP, STRAWBERRY FLAVORED BITS (SUGAR, CORN SYRUP, CORN CEREAL, PARTIALLY HYDROGENATED VEGETABLE OIL (COTTONSEED AND/OR SOYBEAN), MODIFIED FOOD STARCH, CITRIC ACID, NATURAL AND ARTIFICIAL FLAVORS, RED 40, AND BLUE 2), YEAST, BLUEBERRY FLAVORED BITS (SUGAR, CORN SYRUP, MODIFIED FOOD STARCH [CORN], CORN CEREAL, COTTONSEED FIBER, PARTIALLY HYDROGENATED VEGETABLE OIL [COTTONSEED AND/OR SOYBEAN], NATURAL AND ARTIFICIAL FLAVOR, RED 40 LAKE, BLUE 2 LAKE, AND BLUE 1 LAKE), CONTAINS 2% OR LESS OF: STRAWBERRY CONCENTRATE, VITAL WHEAT GLUTEN, SALT, NATURAL AND ARTIFICIAL STRAWBERRY FLAVOR, SOYBEAN OIL, MONO- AND DIGLYCERIDES, SORBIC ACID, DISTILLED MONOGLYCERIDES, PRESERVATIVES (CALCIUM PROPIONATE), XANTHAN GUM, DOUGH CONDITIONERS (CALCIUM SULFATE, L-CYSTEINE), ENZYMES (ENZYMES, WHEAT GLUTEN, MONOGLYCERIDES), EGG YOLK POWDER, RED 40 LAKE (COLOR), YELLOW CORN MEAL.
